<div class="container1">
  <h1 class="text-center">The Original 151 Pokemon</h1>
  <p class="text-center">
    <a href="/pokemon">Favorites</a>
  </p>

  <% pokemon.forEach(function(pokemon) { %>
    <div class="head">
      <h2><%= pokemon.name %></h2>
      <form method="POST" action="/pokemon">
        <input hidden type="text" name="name" value="<%= pokemon.name %>">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Add to Favorite Pokemon</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  <% }); %>
</div>
<div class="container2">
  <h2>Field Journal Entry. Twenty seventh day of February, year of our Lord 1897. </h2>
  <p>It has been three months since my arrival in Kanto. I feel that all my hard work is finally starting to pay off,
    as I have begun to notice creatures of the most peculiar nature. It shall be my greatest joy as a biologist
    to document these new findings. The following pages of this journal shall be intriguing indeed.
   </p>
</div>
